      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This example features crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement for enhanced torsional rigidity. The chassis remains communicative with updated polyurethane bushings and a factory limited-slip differential that provides predictable lock-up. While the exterior shows minor road patina, the drivetrain and suspension geometry are dialed for peak lateral acceleration and performance.",
