    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between a spirited driving experience and daily reliability. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like finish, having been kept in a climate-controlled garage when not in use. Upon close inspection, you may find very minor road-pebble chips on the front bumper and a small hairline scratch near the trunk lid, but the body remains remarkably straight with no dents or fading. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership; the leather upholstery is supple, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Every button, switch, and digital display functions perfectly, including the dual-zone climate control and the premium sound system. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has benefited from regular synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the most recent service included a fresh fluid flush and a comprehensive brake inspection. The engine idles smoothly and pulls with consistent power, while the transmission shifts are sharp and predictable. This is an honest, well-cared-for car looking for an owner who appreciates mechanical integrity and classic styling.",
